<h4>Matchmaking</h4>
<br>I suck at FPS games and I've recently gotten to a point in Tribes where the players have gotten noticably better and I have a hard time keeping up with them.  It has taken me a lot of games to get a win of the day the past few days.  This has caused the game to quickly become less fun and much more frustrating.  The problem is that the matchmaking is just based on level and not actual skill.  I bought the Tribes starter pack, which gives 50% bonus exp, and now I think that might have been a mistake because all it's doing is putting me against better players faster.  I would like to see Tribes matchmaking be based on a skill rating instead of level.  It isn't like League of Legends where anyone below level 30 is just a newb mc uber scrub.
